\cf12 \strokec12 # Executive Summary\cf9 \strokec9 \
\

\f3\i \cf13 \strokec13 >
\f2\i0 \cf9 \strokec9  This document synthesizes infrastructure changes, strategic recommendations, and operational concerns following the Ministry's DevOps deployment activities. We are implementing \cf8 \strokec8 **Big Picture Planning**\cf9 \strokec9  alongside a \cf8 \strokec8 **hybrid Scrum approach**\cf9 \strokec9  to scale uniform agile practices across the ministry\'97cherry-picking proven concepts without adopting prescriptive frameworks.\
\
Our approach emphasizes \cf8 \strokec8 **multi-level backlog refinement**\cf9 \strokec9 , ensuring strategic initiatives (rocks) decompose through the hierarchy into actionable user stories, tasks, and jobs to be done. This creates a continuous delivery culture woven into the team's operational fabric through practical, adaptable Scrum practices.\
\
\cf8 \strokec8 **New:**\cf9 \strokec9  Design tool integration with \cf8 \strokec8 **Figma, Relume, and CodeSpring**\cf9 \strokec9  enables seamless design-to-development handoff, closing the gap between design systems and production code.\
\

