\cf12 \strokec12 # 2. Strategic Recommendations\cf9 \strokec9 \
\
\cf12 \strokec12 ## 2.1 Big Picture Planning: Strategic to Tactical Flow\cf9 \strokec9 \
\
Our Big Picture Planning connects ministry strategy to daily execution through a \cf8 \strokec8 **multi-level backlog hierarchy**\cf9 \strokec9 . Strategic "rocks" (large initiatives) refine through progressive elaboration into deliverable work items.\
\
