| **Quality** | Change Failure Rate | 15% | 10% | 5% |\
| **Quality** | Mean Time to Recovery | 8 hours | 2 hours | 30 minutes |\
| **Business** | Feature Cycle Time | 3 months | 6 weeks | 2 weeks |\
| **Engagement** | Team Velocity Stability | \'b140% | \'b120% | \'b110% |\
| **Design** | **Design-to-Code Lead Time** | **4 weeks** | **1 week** | **3 days** |\
| **Design** | **Design System Consistency** | **60%** | **80%** | **95%** |\
